<subsec:uk-orgs>

[style=nextline]
/ *ME Association*:  #link("https://meassociation.org.uk/") 

One of the two largest UK ME/CFS charities. Provides information, advocacy, and services. Publishes quarterly magazine _ME Essential_. Funds the UK ME/CFS Biobank. Conducted major patient surveys (2010, 2015) documenting treatment experiences. Hosts local support groups nationwide.

